{"data":[{"name":"74:1","price":"盖被的人啊！","arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡمُدَّثِّرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5496,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:2","price":"你应当起来，你应当警告，","arabic":"قُمۡ فَأَنذِرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5497,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:3","price":"你应当颂扬你的养主，","arabic":"وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5498,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:4","price":"你应当洗涤你的衣服，","arabic":"وَثِيَابَكَ فَطَهِّرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5499,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:5","price":"你应当远离污秽，","arabic":"وَٱلرُّجۡزَ فَٱهۡجُرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5500,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:6","price":"你不要施恩而求厚报，","arabic":"وَلَا تَمۡنُن تَسۡتَكۡثِرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5501,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:7","price":"你应当为你的养主而坚忍。","arabic":"وَلِرَبِّكَ فَٱصۡبِرۡ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5502,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:8","price":"当号角被吹响的时候，","arabic":"فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِي ٱلنَّاقُورِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5503,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:9","price":"在那时，将有一个艰难的日子。","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ يَوۡمَئِذٖ يَوۡمٌ عَسِيرٌ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5504,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:10","price":"〔那个日子〕对不归信的人们，是不容易〔渡过的〕。","arabic":"عَلَى ٱلۡكَٰفِرِينَ غَيۡرُ يَسِيرٖ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5505,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:11","price":"你让我独自处治我所创造的那个人吧！","arabic":"ذَرۡنِي وَمَنۡ خَلَقۡتُ وَحِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5506,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:12","price":"我赏赐他丰富的财产，","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡتُ لَهُۥ مَالٗا مَّمۡدُودٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5507,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:13","price":"和在跟前的子嗣，","arabic":"وَبَنِينَ شُهُودٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5508,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:14","price":"我提高了他的声望，","arabic":"وَمَهَّدتُّ لَهُۥ تَمۡهِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5509,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:15","price":"而他还企望我再多加赏赐。","arabic":"ثُمَّ يَطۡمَعُ أَنۡ أَزِيدَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5510,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:16","price":"绝不然！他确是反对我的迹象的，","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ لِأٓيَٰتِنَا عَنِيدٗا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5511,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:17","price":"我将使他遭受苦难。","arabic":"سَأُرۡهِقُهُۥ صَعُودًا","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5512,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:18","price":"他确已思考，确已计划。","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ فَكَّرَ وَقَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5513,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:19","price":"但无论他怎样计划，他是被弃绝的。","arabic":"فَقُتِلَ كَيۡفَ قَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5514,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:20","price":"然后，无论他怎样计划，他终是被弃绝的。","arabic":"ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَيۡفَ قَدَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5515,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:21","price":"他看了看，","arabic":"ثُمَّ نَظَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5516,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:22","price":"然后皱眉蹙额，","arabic":"ثُمَّ عَبَسَ وَبَسَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5517,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:23","price":"然后高傲地转过身去，","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ وَٱسۡتَكۡبَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5518,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:24","price":"而且说：“这只是传习的魔术，","arabic":"فَقَالَ إِنۡ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا سِحۡرٞ يُؤۡثَرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5519,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:25","price":"这只是凡人的言辞。”","arabic":"إِنۡ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا قَوۡلُ ٱلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5520,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:26","price":"我将使他坠入火狱，","arabic":"سَأُصۡلِيهِ سَقَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5521,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:27","price":"你怎能知道火狱是什么？","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا سَقَرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5522,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:28","price":"它不让任何物存在，不许任何物留下，","arabic":"لَا تُبۡقِي وَلَا تَذَرُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5523,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:29","price":"它烧灼肌肤。","arabic":"لَوَّاحَةٞ لِّلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5524,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:30","price":"管理它的，共计十九名。","arabic":"عَلَيۡهَا تِسۡعَةَ عَشَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5525,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:31","price":"我只将管理火狱的造成天使，我只以他们的数目，考验不归信的人们，以便曾受天经的人们认清，而归信的人们更加笃信；以免曾受天经的人们和归信的人们怀疑；以便心中有病者和不归信者说：“安拉设这个譬喻做什么？”安拉这样使他所意欲的人误入迷途，使他所意欲的人遵循正路。只有你的养主，能知道他的军队，这只是人类的教训。","arabic":"وَمَا جَعَلۡنَآ أَصۡحَٰبَ ٱلنَّارِ إِلَّا مَلَٰٓئِكَةٗۖ وَمَا جَعَلۡنَا عِدَّتَهُمۡ إِلَّا فِتۡنَةٗ لِّلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ لِيَسۡتَيۡقِنَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُواْ ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ وَيَزۡدَادَ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓاْ إِيمَٰنٗا وَلَا يَرۡتَابَ ٱلَّذِينَ أُوتُواْ ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ وَٱلۡمُؤۡمِنُونَ وَلِيَقُولَ ٱلَّذِينَ فِي قُلُوبِهِم مَّرَضٞ وَٱلۡكَٰفِرُونَ مَاذَآ أَرَادَ ٱللَّهُ بِهَٰذَا مَثَلٗاۚ كَذَٰلِكَ يُضِلُّ ٱللَّهُ مَن يَشَآءُ وَيَهۡدِي مَن يَشَآءُۚ وَمَا يَعۡلَمُ جُنُودَ رَبِّكَ إِلَّا هُوَۚ وَمَا هِيَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرَىٰ لِلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5526,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:32","price":"真的，以月亮盟誓，","arabic":"كَلَّا وَٱلۡقَمَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5527,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:33","price":"以逝去时的黑夜盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذۡ أَدۡبَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5528,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:34","price":"以显照时的黎明盟誓，","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَآ أَسۡفَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5529,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:35","price":"它〔火狱〕确是一个大难，","arabic":"إِنَّهَا لَإِحۡدَى ٱلۡكُبَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5530,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:36","price":"可以警告人类，","arabic":"نَذِيرٗا لِّلۡبَشَرِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5531,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:37","price":"警告你们中欲前进者或欲后退者；","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَتَقَدَّمَ أَوۡ يَتَأَخَّرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5532,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:38","price":"各人将因自己的营谋而作抵押，","arabic":"كُلُّ نَفۡسِۭ بِمَا كَسَبَتۡ رَهِينَةٌ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5533,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:39","price":"惟右边的人们除外。","arabic":"إِلَّآ أَصۡحَٰبَ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5534,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:40","price":"他们在乐园中互相询问，","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتٖ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5535,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:41","price":"问犯罪人们的情状，","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5536,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:42","price":"“你们为什么堕入火狱呢？”","arabic":"مَا سَلَكَكُمۡ فِي سَقَرَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5537,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:43","price":"他们说：“我们没有礼拜，","arabic":"قَالُواْ لَمۡ نَكُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5538,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:44","price":"也没有济贫，","arabic":"وَلَمۡ نَكُ نُطۡعِمُ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5539,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:45","price":"我们与妄言的人们一道妄言，","arabic":"وَكُنَّا نَخُوضُ مَعَ ٱلۡخَآئِضِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5540,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:46","price":"我们否认报应日，","arabic":"وَكُنَّا نُكَذِّبُ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5541,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:47","price":"一直到死亡降临了我们。”","arabic":"حَتَّىٰٓ أَتَىٰنَا ٱلۡيَقِينُ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5542,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:48","price":"说情者的说情，将无益于他们。","arabic":"فَمَا تَنفَعُهُمۡ شَفَٰعَةُ ٱلشَّٰفِعِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5543,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:49","price":"他们怎么退避这教训呢？","arabic":"فَمَا لَهُمۡ عَنِ ٱلتَّذۡكِرَةِ مُعۡرِضِينَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5544,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:50","price":"他们好像一群惊慌的驴子，","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ حُمُرٞ مُّسۡتَنفِرَةٞ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5545,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:51","price":"刚逃避了一只狮子一样。","arabic":"فَرَّتۡ مِن قَسۡوَرَةِۭ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5546,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:52","price":"不然，他们中的每个人都希望获得一些展开的天经。","arabic":"بَلۡ يُرِيدُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُؤۡتَىٰ صُحُفٗا مُّنَشَّرَةٗ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5547,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:53","price":"绝不然，他们不畏惧后世！","arabic":"كَلَّاۖ بَل لَّا يَخَافُونَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةَ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5548,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:54","price":"真的，这〔《古兰经》〕确是一个教诲！","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهُۥ تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5549,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:55","price":"谁愿意，谁记忆它，","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5550,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"74:56","price":"他们只因安拉的意欲而记忆它。他是应受敬畏的，他是宜于赦宥的。","arabic":"وَمَا يَذۡكُرُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُۚ هُوَ أَهۡلُ ٱلتَّقۡوَىٰ وَأَهۡلُ ٱلۡمَغۡفِرَةِ","category":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir"],"ayahNumber":5551,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["74 (Al-Muddathir)","Al-Muddathir","Surah Al-Muddathir","Chapter Al-Muddathir","Muddathir","Surah Muddathir","Chapter Muddathir","Al Muddathir","Surah Al Muddathir","Chapter Al Muddathir","Surah 74","Chapter 74","The Cloaked One","المدثر"]}